      "MKPD_LTIV_ITEM_ATTR_CNTN": "",
      "MKPD_LTIV_ITEM_CNTN": "<p class=\"ssp-editor-p\"><span>※ 수입인지대금 : 5천 만원 초과시 대출금액별 수입인지비용 차등 부과(50% 균등부담)</span></p><div class=\"table-box\"><table class=\"tbl-matrix\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><thead><tr><th rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 25%;\"><b>대출금액</b></th><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 25%;\"><b>인지세액</b></th></tr><tr><th style=\"width: 25%;\"><b>고객</b></th><th style=\"width: 25%;\"><b>은행</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">5천만원 초과1억원 이하</p></td><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">3만5천원</p></td><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">3만5천원</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">1억원 초과10억원 이하</p></td><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">7만5천원</p></td><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">7만5천원</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">10억원 초과</p></td><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">17만5천원</p></td><td style=\"width: 11.1111%;\"><p class=\"ssp-editor-p\" style=\"text-align: center;\">17만5천원</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
